Package org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.application.ambassador.simulation.navigation

Class RoadPositionFactory

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.application.ambassador.simulation.navigation.RoadPositionFactory
public class RoadPositionFactory extends Object
Factory facade, which generates IRoadPosition in various ways. The IRoadPosition object is mainly used for stop instructions for vehicles.

    • createFromSumoEdge

      public static IRoadPosition createFromSumoEdge(String edgeId, int laneIndex, double edgeOffset)
      Creates a IRoadPosition based on an arbitrary edge ID (= connection ID) in SUMO.
      Parameters:
      edgeId - The id of the edge.
      laneIndex - The index of the lane where the road position is generated at.
      edgeOffset - the offset in m along the edge where the position is generated at
      Returns:
      A new IRoadPosition with all available data.

    • createAlongRoute

      public static IRoadPosition createAlongRoute(IRoadPosition currentPosition, VehicleRoute currentRoute, int laneIndex, double distance)
      Create a IRoadPosition based on the current position of the vehicle and the route its driving on. The position will be generated starting at the position of the vehicle at a given distance along the route.
      Parameters:
      currentPosition - The current position of the vehicle.
      currentRoute - The current route the vehicle driving on.
      laneIndex - The index of lane where the road position is generated at.
      distance - Distance in meters where the road position is generated at, starting from the current position of the vehicle.
      Returns:
      A new IRoadPosition along the given route.

    • createAtEndOfRoute

      public static IRoadPosition createAtEndOfRoute(VehicleRoute currentRoute, int laneIndex)
      Creates an IRoadPosition for the last edge of a list of route nodeIds.
      Parameters:
      currentRoute - The VehicleRoute, that the IRoadPosition should be created for.
      laneIndex - The lane index.
      Returns:
      An IRoadPosition of the last edge in route.
